Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.64,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The bodies were riddled with both \Nknife wounds and bullet holes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.36,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,leading to the conclusion \Nthat they were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.09,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,About a week had passed since their deaths,\Nand the physical damage was severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.95,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The bodies had been unnaturally \Nsewn together with thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:21.24,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Sewn together with thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:26.67,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The couple's daughter, Rachel Gardner, \Nwas found unharmed near their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.88,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,She was escorted to safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.80,italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,but her behavior suggests a \Nstate of confusion, which—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.86,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,The glasses bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:45.56,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we chat in a \Nlittle more depth today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.00,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You don't need to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:53.13,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you looked at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.57,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have such beautiful eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.33,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You see, one of my eyes is artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.68,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I was born missing one eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.04,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It bothered my mother terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.66,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It stressed her out so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.00,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,that her eyes turned very dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.38,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't \Neven see myself in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:20.14,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I loved my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.55,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes were precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.87,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...hate your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.46,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.56,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you do that to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.50,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.57,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You cut and sewed them up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.96,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.84,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,That was because I wanted a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.26,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,What made you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:52.71,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I found a puppy in an alley near our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.69,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,It was tiny and weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.42,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted that puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.89,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,So I was going to ask Mom and Dad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.10,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.73,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is the \Nbreadwinner around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.76,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No one has any need for an alcoholic \Npolice officer like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.97,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.75,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.70,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.82,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been at this hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.46,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping quiet as usual, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.13,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Does your head even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.31,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.63,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.75,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.51,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.65,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you take pleasure in making me miserable?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.94,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.32,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy my own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:05.60,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness? Then buy some\N happiness for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.07,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm miserable, so buy me \Nsome of this "happiness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.12,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.53,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:17.36,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.58,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna get in my way, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.26,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.46,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a filthy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:25.95,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're only going to ruin my \Nlife with your filthy hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.59,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You've torn this family apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:29.88,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.61,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,All that booze has ravaged \Nboth your body and your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.77,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's what made you crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.86,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.52,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.54,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.26,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.20,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.01,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.72,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.39,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.31,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.55,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.41,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.98,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.87,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.58,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.77,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But if I do things without asking \Nyou first, you get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.42,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to ask—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.57,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.05,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you do as I say, either?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:55.46,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of you that I \Ncan't get out of this hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.06,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.09,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.73,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,If I do as you say, will you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.33,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.94,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of them would listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.30,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see the puppy again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.95,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Its little body was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.18,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,And when I tried to pet it, it bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.73,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...remember what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.88,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.18,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I was in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.85,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,...fixing that puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.53,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.85,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.79,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.23,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,That day was really hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.79,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. Good puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.12,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:05.29,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault! She's nuts\N because {\i1}you're{\i0} nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.17,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:10.05,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.63,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check on them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.80,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You made both of us go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.87,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.76,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're like some foul \Nvermin that brings misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.90,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.58,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.12,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.42,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No, stay away... Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:36.37,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,And then... what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.42,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.56,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:09:00.86,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I never needed this in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:05.44,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this house makes me miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.95,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.01,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,...can die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.33,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up, Rachel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.70,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.00,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You think I've gone crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.18,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.38,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.40,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, talking to that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.77,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You did that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.86,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You killed it, then you \Nstitched up its slashed belly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.55,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and sewed its mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.51,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did it make you feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.59,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,This puppy is mine now. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.29,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No one needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.59,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No one needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.74,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.22,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you what that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.87,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:49.36,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She was hiding a thing like that from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.58,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.58,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.02,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Be part of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.84,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,...perfect family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.64,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.11,flashback,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.03,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,...fix you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:21.75,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I sewed my parents' bodies together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.73,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I replaced Dad's bad arm with a stuffed arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:32.51,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,and I stitched up Mom's mouth to \Nmake it look like she was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.31,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I made them the perfect Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.68,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.76,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Then the three of us played \Nwith the puppy and had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:47.10,italics,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,So when the police took them away, I was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.90,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel, I understand your sadness very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.54,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:01.07,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Another small animal died at the \Norphanage you stayed in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.40,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why it died?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.76,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.54,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were taking care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.41,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.80,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.68,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,No use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.57,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.51,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I could make it my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.43,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:35.19,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.07,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing worked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:45.28,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, do you want more \Nthings to call your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:52.00,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel, my mother committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:56.33,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,My eye killed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:01.73,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look exactly like hers \Ndid the last time I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:06.34,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,They're dark, silent,\Nand above all, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.54,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I love your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:12.14,italics,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,That dark radiance in \Nyour eyes will forever—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.65,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to mean \NI know all about Ray now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.32,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of showing me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:29.24,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, screw that eyeball freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.84,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.16,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rough, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.08,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,The door's already unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.02,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Zack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:51.09,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Ray. Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:55.52,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kill all the people \Nwho come to this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.19,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.19,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.24,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rough with Rachel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.87,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.63,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you know everything now, Zack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.80,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,That was some pretty sick shit you showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.97,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. It's my job, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.99,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.01,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gotten my answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:38.98,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kill everyone who comes here, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.78,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna kill me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.15,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.03,top,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.22,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.70,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.58,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.08,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Zack, everything is just as you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:01.96,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:10.59,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. We don't need to \Ntalk about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:16.06,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,The priest made her this floor's \Nresident at my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:20.24,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,But she had a mental breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.77,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,All over a single Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.35,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You were always so calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What made you lose your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.69,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted the things \Nthat I'd consider perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.49,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't allow it to be any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.54,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But it said in the Bible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:45.63,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,...that the one who could really \Nnever be forgiven was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:50.26,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you wanted \NZack to kill you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.89,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you know, Rachel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:57.99,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,that no matter how much you read the \NBible or realize your own mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.44,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,that feeling you have won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:06.20,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how absolutely awful and wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.03,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Zack, you get it now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.00,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to choose your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.57,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You can be killed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:18.02,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,or you can give up on being \NRachel's God and leave here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.12,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.25,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Is what he's saying true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.97,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,She deceived you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.38,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.26,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Zack...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.64,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Will you continue to be my God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.86,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get me \Nto make your decisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.03,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...not your God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.91,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.10,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel, now you can be your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.42,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grant any wish you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:10.47,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unclean. I've sinned. \NI've always known that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.74,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.25,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,just knowing something is a sin makes it bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.82,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Zack, you won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.90,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,You really won't be my God?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.86,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.03,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But I want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.28,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I want my own God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.91,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,That's not loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.37,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I loaded it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:45.96,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:52.76,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rachel! Your eyes look more \Nbeautiful in this moment than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:57.22,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Rachel! Rachel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.14,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Zack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.35,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd let you go, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:06.40,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,My top priority right now is what {\i1}she{\i0} wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.23,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.00,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.44,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:20.15,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful eyes you have, Rachel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.16,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll grant your wish for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.53,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.24,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Ray! Don't you run from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.37,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start playing with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.04,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,You still hate fire, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.95,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Enough of this shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.13,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:23.80,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.15,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.87,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep running around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:47.44,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.04,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die now, Zack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.54,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you're gonna kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.78,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll just kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.30,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good enough anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:04.01,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I still believe that I need to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.18,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,that I need to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.35,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm unclean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.73,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,God doesn't want even that much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.69,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:23.46,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, it was you who promised to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.41,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,But when I found out there was no God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.43,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,you became my new God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.62,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.71,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.92,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.51,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,When the lie was exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.05,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,...my new God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.65,main,Rachel,0000,0000,0000,,...died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.91,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.37,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep saying whatever \Nyou want and running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:20.73,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,All you ever do is run away, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.53,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:28.01,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,She has nothing more to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.91,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,You're not usually this unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:33.96,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.48,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Get violent, and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:40.01,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel, this is taking a bit too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.94,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.57,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he {\i1}is{\i0} a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I supposed it can't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.64,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.62,main,Danny,0000,0000,0000,,If you put a bullet through his head \Nfrom this distance, he's sure to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.91,main,Zack,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
